Feature: Signing up for newsletter

  Scenario: User signing up for newsletter with valid emailID
    Given user if at home layout8 page
    When user enters valid email address "harinignanam2305@gmail.com"
    And clicks subscribe
    Then user should see message subscription successfull

  Scenario: User signing up for newsletter with existing emailID
    Given user if at home layout8 page
    When user enters existing email address "harinignanam2305@gmail.com"
    And clicks subscribe
    Then user should see message email already exist

  Scenario: User signing up for newsletter with invalid emailID
    Given user if at home layout8 page
    When user enters valid email address "hhjsjlslsksdj"
    And clicks subscribe
    Then user should see message invalid email